conditiontext:
All components are present and bagged. This game has known issues with the miniatures and there are a couple in this set. The Witch King is missing his left forearm/hand, the Ringwraiths are missing 2 out of 3 swords, and Gothmog's ax head is broken. The other 7 miniatures are intact. I have all the broken pieces except for 1 Ringwraith sword so they can be repaired.

The box has significant wear. One corner is split with some dishing of the lid. Two corners are split on the box bottom as well as a small break in a bottom edge seam. Let me know if you would like photos.
